b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2113,"category_name":"Events","pr_category_id":"4","title_name":"A New Quest, Trials of the Mighty, Is Here!","message":"<div>A new series of quests, Trials of the Mighty, debuted on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1617775200\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/e3feafd9615f9e914c5a00e4639ba0a9.png\\"><\/div><div>In Trials of the Mighty, you&#39;ll be challenged to take on various bosses with a team of one or more predetermined elements and weapon types. Clear these quests to earn rewards like materials for unlocking the mana spirals of certain adventurers (called &quot;convictions&quot; and &quot;devotions&quot; that are that unique to each adventurer) from the daily bonus.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/4c7900585c895e13f7c3b28c17c36cf1.png\\"><\/div><div>Suggested might for Thor&#39;s Trial: Standard (Light): 15,000<\/div><div>Suggested might for Thor&#39;s Trial: Expert (Light): 20,000<\/div><div>Suggested might for Thor&#39;s Trial: Master (Light): 38,000<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Quest Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1617775200\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618379999\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Eligible Element and Weapon Types<\/div><div>Shadow, Sword\/Wand\/Staff<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Eligible Convictions and Devotions<\/div><div>Gala Prince&#39;s<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/f2e39c74edf05dc1236321f62524aa50.png\\"><\/div><div>Suggested might for Poseidon&#39;s Trial: Standard (Water): 15,000<\/div><div>Suggested might for Poseidon&#39;s Trial: Expert (Water): 20,000<\/div><div>Suggested might for Poseidon&#39;s Trial: Master (Water): 38,000<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Quest Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618380000\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618984799\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Eligible Element and Weapon Types<\/div><div>Wind, Dagger\/Wand\/Staff<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Eligible Convictions and Devotions<\/div><div>Gala Elisanne&#39;s<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/234ccdfc6b52bd7382ba733512802478.png\\"><\/div><div>Suggested might for Zephyr&#39;s Trial: Standard (Wind): 15,000<\/div><div>Suggested might for Zephyr&#39;s Trial: Expert (Wind): 20,000<\/div><div>Suggested might for Zephyr&#39;s Trial: Master (Wind): 38,000<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Quest Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1618984800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1619589599\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Eligible Element and Weapon Types<\/div><div>Flame, Axe\/Lance\/Staff<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Eligible Convictions and Devotions<\/div><div>Gala Ranzal&#39;s<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Daily Bonus<\/div><div>Materials for unlocking the mana spirals of certain adventurers (called &quot;convictions&quot; and &quot;devotions&quot; that are that unique to each adventurer) are available from the daily bonus. Rewards from the daily bonus are obtained automatically when earned.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Note that the daily bonus for Trials of the Mighty differs from the traditional daily bonus in that players may stock multiple unearned bonuses. This stock grows incrementally by one every day at 07:00 (up to a maximum of three).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Daily bonus rewards depend on the quest difficulty and are as follows:<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbStandard: Eligible adventurer&#39;s Conviction &times; 1, Nature&#39;s Blessing &times; 1, Fortifying Dragonscale &times; 2, Amplifying Dragonscale &times; 2<\/div><div>\\u30fbExpert: Eligible adventurer&#39;s Conviction &times; 2, eligible adventurer&#39;s Devotion &times; 1, Nature&#39;s Blessing &times; 1, Fortifying Dragonscale &times; 2, Amplifying Dragonscale &times; 2<\/div><div>\\u30fbMaster: Eligible adventurer&#39;s Conviction &times; 2, eligible adventurer&#39;s Devotion &times; 1, Nature&#39;s Blessing &times; 2, Fortifying Dragonscale &times; 3, Amplifying Dragonscale &times; 3<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The reward from each daily bonus depends on the boss who was defeated when it is earned. For example, if you stock a daily bonus while Thor&#39;s Trial is available, then earn it while Poseidon&#39;s Trial is available, you will earn the rewards from Poseidon&#39;s Trial, not Thor&#39;s Trial.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Note: Players must have completed up to Chapter 10 \/ 6-3 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1617775200,"prev_article_id":"2112","next_article_id":"2114","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/e3feafd9615f9e914c5a00e4639ba0a9.png","update_time":1617594252}}}'